OL,3,CMenai Suspension Bridge to close for
OL,4,Crepairs to fix 'safety risk'
OL,6,FThe Menai Suspension Bridge will fully
OL,7,Fclose for one day, with longer
OL,8,Fclosures for a single lane, as the
OL,9,Fsecond stage of repair works begin.
OL,11,FThe full closure comes after an
OL,12,F"immediate safety risk" was found with
OL,13,Fthe communication cables under the
OL,14,Fbridge, resulting in scaffolding
OL,15,Fneeding to be installed.
OL,17,FThe cables provide communication links
OL,18,Fbetween Anglesey and Ireland and must
OL,19,Fbe fixed before further work to the
OL,20,Fbridge can continue.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
