OL,3,CMenai Suspension Bridge to close for
OL,4,Crepairs to fix 'safety risk'
OL,6,FThe bridge will fully close from 2pm
OL,7,Fon Friday, 15 May until 6pm on
OL,8,FSaturday, 16 May.
OL,10,FThere will also be a single lane
OL,11,Fclosure on the bridge which will be in
OL,12,Fplace until 22 May between 10am and
OL,13,F6pm each day.
OL,15,FWalkers and dismounted cyclists will
OL,16,Fbe still able to cross the bridge
OL,17,Fduring the maintenance works.
OL,19,FDiversion will be available via the
OL,20,FBritannia Bridge.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
